28
00:04:19,635 --> 00:04:22,721
It's not San Quentin.
It's a nut house.

29
00:04:22,846 --> 00:04:25,849
Most patients don't know where
they are. They won't hurt you.

30
00:04:25,933 --> 00:04:29,019
