if you had it to do over again,
would you do it the same way?

164
00:14:46,094 --> 00:14:48,096
I reckon I would.

165
00:14:49,848 --> 00:14:52,017
Anyhow, they put me in here...

166
00:14:52,351 --> 00:14:55,479
